body:
I am trying to import an existing idf geometry file from Openstudio and everytime I look at the model in Rhino, the rooms are on-top of one another.

I tried importing a few idf files from the EPlus example directory and from DesignBuilder, both work much better and give geometry that matches the layout of thermal zones.

Is there anything I am missing in my model? or in how the import idf function works?
